48/*
49 * Global variables. Defined in aslmain.c only, externed in all other files
50 */
51
52#undef ASL_EXTERN
53
54#ifdef _DECLARE_GLOBALS
55#define ASL_EXTERN
56#define ASL_INIT_GLOBAL(a,b) (a)=(b)
57#else
58#define ASL_EXTERN extern
59#define ASL_INIT_GLOBAL(a,b) (a)
60#endif
